Requires GLM, glfw 3, glload and glimg to compile.

Unless stated in credits.txt all the objects and textures in the resources
folder were created for this project.

----Controls----
Press T for tour
Press E to exit tour
Press Space to pause or resume motion
Press H to display the help text in the console
Press Q or Esc to exit
Press Left to rotate camera to the left
Press Right to rotate camera to the right
Press Up to speed up forward motion
Press Down to slow down forward motion
Press Page Up to increase the camera elevation
Press Page Down to reduce the camera elevation